data.title: Baburam Bhattarai
data.text:
PM Dahal, 3 former PMs scheduled to address election gathering in Chitwan today

Apr 20, 2023

Prime Minister Pushpa Kamal Dahal 'Prachanda' and three former PMs are scheduled to address an election rally today here in Chitwan.

Nepali Congress has secured a mayoral seat in Butwal Sub Metropolitan City. Khel Raj Pandey, who contested in the May 13 local election

Nov 9, 2021

Former Prime Minister and Chairperson of Janata Samajwadi Party, Nepal Baburam Bhattarai has said that a stable government cannot be made in the country until the implementation of a directly-elected executive presidential system.

Judgment in the case of Baburam Bhattarai and Madhav Kumar Nepal is scheduled to come on November 15.

Bhattarai says court has interpreted the constitution as per its spirit

Jul 18, 2021

Chairperson of the Federal Council of Janata Samajbadi Party-Nepal, Baburam Bhattarai, has stated the Supreme Court has interpreted the constitution as per its spirit.

JSP Chairperson Yadav seeks Foreign Ministry portfolio

Jul 13, 2021

The Upendra Yadav-led faction of Janata Samajbadi Party-Nepal has decided to join the government that is to be led by Nepali Congress President Sher Bahadur Deuba.

Royal massacre should be investigated, says Bhattarai

Jun 3, 2021

Bhattarai has tweeted that an investigation committee should be set up based on national consensus for the purpose.
